  <description><![CDATA[<p><span>Set sail on a seven-night exploration of the </span><a data-udi="umb://document/c2a0cfb0af8146d18a45e08bc4c22d42" href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/sicily/aeolian-islands" title="Aeolian Islands">Aeolian Islands</a><span>, touring the stunning volcanic Archipelago in the Tyrrhenian Sea. Head to the waters aboard a Gulet boat, which is a traditional wooden Turkish yacht. Travelling by sea and staying in a comfortable cabin on board, makes for unique and memorable way to explore the seven UNESCO World Heritage islands off the coast of Sicily. Get ready to experience the jaw dropping landscapes and make memories that you will never forget. You’ll have the chance to climb up Vulcano and Stromboli, explore the beautiful island of Liapri, visit the smallest of the seven islands Panarea, see the lava scree of </span><em>Sciara del Fuoco </em>burst<span>fiery molten lava into the nights sky and explore the lush landscapes and fresh water springs of Salina.</span></p>
<div>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/sailing-the-aeolian-islands#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/sailing-the-aeolian-islands#Itinerary&quot;">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/sailing-the-aeolian-islands#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/sailing-the-aeolian-islands#Hotels">Hotels</a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/sailing-the-aeolian-islands#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
